{"tid":108091,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"唔知幾時開始 拍拖唔係兩個人既事","createTime":"2017-02-05T03:19:35.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-17T15:39:16.000Z","uid":72212,"like":13,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"314e26af7a397e78b3f5cefe0ba91b13cdff4133","tid":108091,"uid":72212,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-05T03:19:35.000Z","msg":"有留意我之前幾個post都知<br />\n呢一排有個經歷令我好深刻<br />\n細細個a0果陣以為自己同鍾意一齊既人就夠<br />\n根本唔洗點諗其他野 手拖手已經好開心<br />\n大個左 中學 要理屋企人 其次朋友 其實都幾大壓力<br />\n仲要唔知幾時開始 天真純情既愛無左<br />\n唔知邊個話有愛就一定要有性咁 呢個問題都係其次<br />\n<br />\n直到今年 我又明多一樣野<br />\n我都講過我係自己住又有養寵物<br />\n但係我第一篇文個男仔<br />\n佢又好想24小時痴實我既<br />\n但係呢個無可能架嘛<br />\n我都有自己生活圈子 屋企 住既地方<br />\n直到佢屋企人搵我傾計<br />\n真係好大壓力<br />\n既然佢屋企人話講啲野無乜含意<br />\n但竟然可以講左4粒鍾黎黎去去果幾樣野<br />\n錢錢錢錢同錢咁<br />\n1.做人有乜目標呀?講完目標又要話進步自己個目標<br />\n2.做乜租屋咁笨柒呀?<br />\n3.養寵物都可以搬去公屋姐?<br />\n大佬養寵物一世架 責任黎架.<br />\n認真 相處耐左有感情 我隻寵物最重要<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n4.你知唔知我間屋啲水電點黎架?<br />\n5.你入得黎呢間屋就要點點點!<br />\n6.我死左 飯錢咁點算呀? 點生活呀?<br />\n哇...真係難聽過粗口 仲有好多未打<br />\n我問朋友借都唔用你啲錢啦<br />\n講到白食白住咁 家陣無貼錢養你個仔架我?<br />\n我自己租屋唔係因為拍拖都唔過黎訓啦<br />\n講到我自己無屋企咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n算啦講到1999....<br />\n希望大家明我講啲乜啦<br />\n無野既純粹發洩下..<br />\n想拍個拖都要面對咁既野 真係好大壓力好辛苦"},{"pid":"52d0a1118f5f9616317b5a0a7098781a1eb07c8a","tid":108091,"uid":30778,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-05T03:25:32.000Z","msg":"你住係人地屋企？<br />\n<br />\n你男朋友想痴實你，你又唔想有說話聽，大家一齊出去租屋住啦"},{"pid":"da3a995a6c9c6a014fdfde4293b6ae3d8f31285c","tid":108091,"uid":72212,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-05T03:51:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你住係人地屋企？<br />\n<br />\n你男朋友想痴實你，你又唔想有說話聽，大家一齊出去租屋住啦</blockquote><br />\n分左手啦 我自己有租屋 佢唔黎住<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1a7870e4b1e1395de852ed084833de4cc7b63a4a","tid":108091,"uid":72769,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-05T04:05:27.000Z","msg":"岩呀 點解唔可以兩個人開開心心咁拍拖<br />\n先拍幾個月 驚死我騙財騙色咁<br />\n講野難聽過屎<br />\n可以唔洗其他人感受既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"71e02f55f8bb10e764b2f53754b019d50fdf3c9d","tid":108091,"uid":66625,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-05T04:22:35.000Z","msg":"越大個就越多野要顧慮 好想可以簡簡單單鍾意就一齊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e94c4a878f95129c992c198dbc10f0997cd3ed9d","tid":108091,"uid":19065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-05T04:31:02.000Z","msg":"同意 去個旅行又怕我搞大佢知女個肚又怕扑左又盛<br />\n大佬呀, 香港扑野有幾難,"},{"pid":"1c2b92d521b3db6176dbf6e05cb015f4b0e0c181","tid":108091,"uid":72769,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-05T05:09:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>同意 去個旅行又怕我搞大佢知女個肚又怕扑左又盛<br />\n大佬呀, 香港扑野有幾難,</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n最後有冇去到？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"03b4ff716474e307b24a9b79e398b36efffede2d","tid":108091,"uid":72212,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-05T05:23:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>同意 去個旅行又怕我搞大佢知女個肚又怕扑左又盛<br />\n大佬呀, 香港扑野有幾難,</blockquote><br />\n成年人扑野識安全就得啦 講起扑野 日日問我有無避孕<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n心諗大左肚果個係我 男人驚啲咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"65acd1842055c9a83c23f6ce8c77b7a2ba4c0c4c","tid":108091,"uid":72212,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-05T05:24:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>越大個就越多野要顧慮 好想可以簡簡單單鍾意就一齊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n所以多數分手收場<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我只可以話有緣無份 時間錯左"},{"pid":"193c6a16f06be4b7343dd2f59f5eca786f640925","tid":108091,"uid":72212,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-05T05:25:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>岩呀 點解唔可以兩個人開開心心咁拍拖<br />\n先拍幾個月 驚死我騙財騙色咁<br />\n講野難聽過屎<br />\n可以唔洗其他人感受既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n朋友可以唔理 人地屋企好難唔理 話哂外人<br />\n自己屋企就話最親 實幫自己架姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1f61433d6982f15a63b968726b3c8c4c0e2ffd6b","tid":108091,"uid":72212,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-05T07:49:25.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"a4e5746a4fe2f29d04b4b6db959508e78e795aaa","tid":108091,"uid":72769,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-05T07:57:45.000Z","msg":"如果一開始對方家庭已經唔中意 可以點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n仲要無意中聽到啲好難聽既說話 要扮聽唔到"},{"pid":"5c37a7d6781dc9f6a96ac4d260afd017cb5cdcc3","tid":108091,"uid":72212,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-05T10:06:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>如果一開始對方家庭已經唔中意 可以點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n仲要無意中聽到啲好難聽既說話 要扮聽唔到</blockquote><br />\n唯有係咁<br />\n我係一開始無問題 但愈來愈多說話聽"},{"pid":"e3b8c898437c2b03d69a7faef4d27469dfd97c31","tid":108091,"uid":72212,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-05T11:00:28.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"168936157413dfb5b3f3c972cdb3ce1d084028ae","tid":108091,"uid":72212,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-05T11:01:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>如果一開始對方家庭已經唔中意 可以點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n仲要無意中聽到啲好難聽既說話 要扮聽唔到</blockquote><br />\n唔係三口六面點名對住黎講<br />\n又好鍾意條女既就忍下啦"},{"pid":"2caafa4bd42348c49ca46a6acb2af60daa15eebe","tid":108091,"uid":72212,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-06T08:39:54.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"7ab24863c71aaf0d9721f081dc6096e3e5aff897","tid":108091,"uid":53122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-06T10:10:50.000Z","msg":"其實係你鍾意d 裙脚仔<br />\n咩都聽屋企話<br />\n<br />\n唔係話唔孝順屋企<br />\n<br />\n只不過連自己條女都保護唔到要佢受自己屋企嘅氣<br />\n<br />\ndd 男人你都唔駛旨意佢有咩擔當<br />\n早飛早著"},{"pid":"24399ed4d7ada3dbaafc0e546a9aaa4f82045888","tid":108091,"uid":53122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-06T10:14:49.000Z","msg":"你條仔聽到老母對你單單打打<br />\n<br />\n係關心你嘅愛惜你嘅<br />\n<br />\n即刻反枱屌佢老母啦 <br />\n<br />\n聽到都無動作或叫你忍吓<br />\n<br />\n佢好明顯只係鍾意屌你<br />\n唔係鍾意你"},{"pid":"c915fbf2e71f75b4d64460b990195c3d2e3dfda2","tid":108091,"uid":16740,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-06T10:19:17.000Z","msg":"原本兩個人既事，變左好多人既事"},{"pid":"e78a3c858de7b3106273ecd6d9db7b70f8fca6ef","tid":108091,"uid":72212,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-07T04:31:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你條仔聽到老母對你單單打打<br />\n<br />\n係關心你嘅愛惜你嘅<br />\n<br />\n即刻反枱屌佢老母啦 <br />\n<br />\n聽到都無動作或叫你忍吓<br />\n<br />\n佢好明顯只係鍾意屌你<br />\n唔係鍾意你</blockquote><br />\n老豆老母都有野聽 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n不過算啦 都完左"},{"pid":"a82ad6015e02c656aa86da10916c3265bd099acb","tid":108091,"uid":10694,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-07T05:34:25.000Z","msg":"我情況都相類似<br />\n佢媽咪有d 反對我地拍拖...<br />\n因為職業,加上對我印象分麻麻<br />\n依家半分手狀態<br />\n分開左但又keep 住聯絡,出街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8e58e147c68742d412a08143fd41aceaa6d73b7e","tid":108091,"uid":72212,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-07T07:44:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4002d132d883087071cbe9db98758cb83d917461","tid":108091,"uid":72212,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-07T15:47:50.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"4fa8cd49e7456c5ae01c6c057ba598682c366b29","tid":108091,"uid":72212,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"cited